# Secure Azure Infrastructure & Telemetry Pipeline (Multi-Phase Project)

This repository contains a full, multi-phase Azure security and observability project.  
It starts with a secure VM deployment (no public IP), continues with private networking, monitoring, AMA+DCR telemetry, and ends with a complete Sentinel analytics pipeline.


